      "created_at": "2022-12-05T16:29:43.870Z",
      "cooked": "<p>I\u2019ve tried that - I may be missing something but it never asks about the distance type of event.  If it is a 100 mile ride where is that accounted for?  Just \u201clong day\u201d as the peak type?  I would think the distance is important in the build period as well but I don\u2019t see that.  I am new to biking - long distance running in the past - but would expect some of the distance accounted for in the build period.</p>",
