      "created_at": "2022-12-05T16:57:43.946Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Distance is less relevant and it does ask expected duration.  Generally you want to slowly build up a weekly long ride until you get to around 50-70% of the event duration as similar to riding terrain as possible. Right now the consistency and not doing too much too soon is most important.  Later in the last 4-8 weeks prior to the even you need to get more specific.</p>",
